<div id="getting-started">
  <p>
    This <a href="http://ld4l.org">LD4L</a> Demonstration Search is demonstration application providing a search service over linked open data from the catalogs of <a href="https://newcatalog.library.cornell.edu/">Cornell</a>, <a href="http://library.harvard.edu/">Harvard</a>, and <a href="https://searchworks.stanford.edu/">Stanford</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    The data is a snapshot that will not be kept up-to-date, and the search is not linked to the live catalogs of the three institutions.
  </p>
<p>
  This is a <a href="http://projectblacklight.org/">Blacklight</a> application based on a <a href="https://lucene.apache.org/solr/">Solr</a> index. The index was built by extracting data from a triplestore containing snapshot data from the three institutions according to the <a href="http://bib.ld4l.org/ontology">LD4L ontology</a>.
</div>

<script>
  $(function() {
    $('#about a').on('click', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();

      if ($('#about-content').html() == "") {
        $('#about-content').load($(this).attr("href"), function() {
          $('#about-content').show();
        });
      } else {
        $('#about-content').toggle();
      }
    });
  });
</script>